      <title>github+hexo搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/07/github-hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/07/github-hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言："><a href="#前言：" class="headerlink" title="前言："></a>前言：</h3><p>​        随着互联网浪潮的翻腾，国内外涌现出越来越多优秀的社交网站让用户分享信息更加便捷。一名真正的程序猿或许可以自己动手编写一个属于自己的博客网站，然而，我只是一名半路出家的半程序猿，也想要拥有一个属于自己的博客网站，写写文章记录自己的生活、工作、学习等。</p><p>​        花了几天时间学习基于github+hexo搭建个人博客，并安装butterfly主题，在此，写下简易搭建完博客的正式第一篇博客，记录此过程。</p><h3 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h3><p>​        Hexo是一款基于Node.js的静态博客框架，依赖少，易于安装使用，可以方便的生成静态网页托管在GitHub和Heroku上，是搭建博客的首选框架。同时，可以更换不同主题，自定义各种样式。</p><p>Hexo主题<a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">theme</a></p><h3 id="博客环境搭建"><a href="#博客环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="博客环境搭建"></a>博客环境搭建</h3><p>博客搭建需要的两个软件：</p><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/">Node.js</a><br><a href="https://git-scm.com/">git</a></p><p>修改配置文件用到的软件：</p><p><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">vscode</a> : 适合有开发基础的程序猿，非常好用。</p><h4 id="下载Git和Node-js"><a href="#下载Git和Node-js" class="headerlink" title="下载Git和Node.js"></a>下载Git和Node.js</h4><p>Node.js与Git安装教程  (<a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MjU4NzI2NA==&amp;mid=2247493430&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1587f3adb7f73919ccfbecff557229a3&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MjU4NzI2NA==&amp;mid=2247493430&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1587f3adb7f73919ccfbecff557229a3&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect</a>)</p><h4 id="Hexo安装"><a href="#Hexo安装" class="headerlink" title="Hexo安装"></a>Hexo安装</h4><p><strong>注意</strong>：由于npm是从国外服务器下载，受网络影响较大，可能会出现异常，所以我们需要连接国内淘宝官方镜像服务器来进行：在新建的blog文件内右击鼠标—&gt;Git Bash Here ,然后输入以下命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-g</span> cnpm <span class="token parameter variable">--registry</span><span class="token operator">=</span>https://registry.npm.taobao.org<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>如果运行上述命令后，后续使用命令<strong>cnpm</strong>开头</p><p>hexo安装<strong>此处有两种方案：（推荐第二种）</strong></p><p>1、选一个磁盘作为博客文件存放位置，新建一个文件夹（例如：<strong>blog</strong>），创建完后，不要进入该文件夹内，在创建该文件夹处，右击鼠标—&gt;Git Bash Here ,然后输入以下命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># hexo框架安装</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-g</span> hexo-cli<span class="token comment"># 安装完成hexo后，输入下面的命令 ，此处新建文件夹为blog</span>hexo init <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>新建文件夹的名称<span class="token operator">&gt;</span>  <span class="token builtin class-name">cd</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>新建文件夹名称<span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token comment">#安装博客所需的依赖文件</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>2、选一个磁盘作为博客文件存放位置，新建一个文件夹（例如：<strong>blog</strong>），进入该文件夹内，右击鼠标—&gt;Git Bash Here ,然后输入以下命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment"># hexo框架安装</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-g</span> hexo-cli<span class="token comment">#上面命令运行完后，输入下面的命令</span>hexo init<span class="token comment">#安装博客所需依赖文件</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>安装完成后，此时blog文件夹内多了许多文件，站点目录如下：</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95.png" alt="站点目录"></p><p><strong>注意：</strong>后续命令均在<strong>站点目录</strong>下（即<strong>blog文件内</strong>）使用<strong>Git Bash</strong>运行。</p><p>此时，hexo本地博客框架搭建已经完成，运行如下命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment">#静态文件生成 hexo generate 简写 hexo g</span>hexo g<span class="token comment">#启动本地服务器 hexo server  简写 hexo s</span>hexo s<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>说明：如果没有server，则需要安装hexo-server插件</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment">#安装hexo-server插件</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-server <span class="token parameter variable">--save</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>运行完hexo s命令后，出现如下图：</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/hexo-s.png" alt="image-hexo -s"></p><p>浏览器中打开&lt;http：//localhost:4000&gt;,可以看到一个网页，说明hexo博客已经成功在本地运行。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/hexo.png" alt="image-hexo"></p><h4 id="博客部署到Github-Pages"><a href="#博客部署到Github-Pages" class="headerlink" title="博客部署到Github Pages"></a>博客部署到Github Pages</h4><p>上述步骤，本地博客成功搭建，接下来将本地博客发布到github pages，然后可以共享至其他人观看。</p><p>首先需要安装发布的插件，在站点目录下执行下面的命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-deployer-git <span class="token parameter variable">--save</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>将本地目录与github关联起来，输入下面命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">ssh-keygen <span class="token parameter variable">-t</span> rsa <span class="token parameter variable">-C</span> <span class="token string">"你的注册邮箱"</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>四个回车键之后完成密钥生成，该密钥文件在如下图位置：</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/ssh.png" alt="image-ssh"></p><p>然后在C:/Users/[username]目录下找到名为.ssh的文件夹， 文件夹内会有两个文件，一个<strong>id_rsa.pub</strong>一个<strong>id_rsa</strong>，用文本编辑器打开<strong>id_rsa.pub</strong>，复制里面的的内容。然后打开Github，点击右上角的头像<strong>Settings</strong> 选择<strong>SSH and GPG keys</strong>。<strong><strong>点击</strong>New SSH key<strong>将之前复制的内容粘帖到Key的框中。上面的</strong>Title<strong>可以随意，点击</strong>Add SSH key<strong>完成添加。</strong></strong></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/github_ssh.png" alt="image-20221007184302429"></p><p>回到bash 界面，测试是否与github链接成功，输入如下命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">ssh</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-T</span> git@github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>点击回车，然后会出现一个询问内容，输入<strong>yes</strong>，回车，会出现一段内容，**Hi <account name="">! You’ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub doesnot provide shell access.<strong>。说明连接成功。此处这个</strong><account name="">**应该是你Github的用户名。</account></account></p><h5 id="github新建一个仓库"><a href="#github新建一个仓库" class="headerlink" title="github新建一个仓库"></a><strong>github新建一个仓库</strong></h5><p><strong>注意：</strong>仓库名格式为：用户名.github.io，此名即为后续博客域名，通过https://用户名.github.io即可访问该博客。</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/github_newrep.png" alt="image-20221007185454817"></p><p>使用vscode打开站点目录下_config.yml文件，拖到文件末尾，修改deploy属性：</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/1285057792/Image/7af31553d6fb0287341186da1e10927f095846e8/deploy%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7.png" alt="image-20221007190133755"></p><p>此时需要安装一个deploy插件，输入命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">cnpm <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-deployer-git<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h5 id="博客部署"><a href="#博客部署" class="headerlink" title="博客部署"></a>博客部署</h5><p>将本地博客部署到github pages，输入命令：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment">#将本地文件部署到github </span>hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>至此，整个博客建站，部署等已经完成，此时回到浏览器输入：https://用户名.github.io，即可访问你的博客。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
